y=\\frac{1}{-x}$ 的平移可得到 $f(x)$ ，则此时 $f(x)$ 单调递增, 作出图像如下图所示,\n\n第二步:\n令\n\n$$\ng(x)=f(x)-m x+\\frac{2}{3} m=0\n$$\n\n即\n![","target":"https://cdn.mathpix.com/cropped/2024_10_24_47a253f79e08acf28419g-26.jpg?height=429&width=577&top_left_y=314&top_left_x=1342","line":526}],"task_lines":[],"tasks":{},"codeblock_ranges":[],"last_embed":{"hash":"3nne2h","at":1771320440961}},"smart_blocks:10-试卷汇总/试卷 md 版本/功底考16题1-16套.md#科目二答题示例": {"path":null,"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.08151954,-0.00338523,0.03509863,-0.07070105,-0.00432045,0.01391348,0.00077039,-0.02550434,0.02118797,-0.00829933,0.03330327,-0.03052929,0.04492183,-0.0048074,0.02131271,0.0429902,-0.03504601,-0.02133914,-0.07800993,0.00792946,0.12893218,-0.02778525,0.00279425,-0.05064287,0.01946011,0.04851722,0.00713935,-0.02303635,-0.01063563,-0.1870597,0.00302525,0.00846097,-0.01077092,0.0319434,0.03825236,-0.06251015,-0.02315683,0.06717802,-0.06761341,0.0394812,0.00002274,0.06225483,0.07011188,-0.02938981,0.00073667,-0.0419391,-0.02156658,-0.0281319,0.03603341,-0.04149108,-0.04528772,-0.02042788,-0.02361172,0.03088378,0.02981414,-0.00709565,-0.0157632,0.07950556,0.02896756,-0.03935019,0.04529881,0.03301153,-0.22483352,0.00891048,0.05609293,-0.01425904,-0.01259327,-0.03368704,0.04045429,0.05570808,-0.04625854,0.01428811,0.01480308,0.04419405,-0.02383766,-0.02289957,0.04761043,-0.01736511,-0.06738368,-0.01702509,-0.02103254,0.07921241,0.03748418,-0.01328511,-0.00255556,0.00994271,0.02211132,-0.04706552,-0.02015337,-0.05770193,-0.01646673,-0.00753464,-0.00455851,0.05593132,-0.0463475,0.00639136,0.03949267,0.02931906,-0.02224783,0.10069867,-0.02799637,0.08663298,-0.01434799,-0.11209846,0.00207731,-0.04921604,-0.02604351,-0.073074,-0.04405643,-0.03425716,-0.04310323,-0.02252137,0.07956733,-0.07007147,-0.01651602,-0.02147111,0.07845954,0.03558863,-0.03653484,-0.03238965,0.03653529,0.04854724,0.04075867,-0.03256301,-0.0073252,-0.05901787,0.0320512,-0.00229054,0.06011569,0.05380063,0.04419905,-0.01258889,0.0